<title>aria2c</title>
<p>This page explains all options for configuring aria2c in Preferences in <app>Parabolic</app>.</p>

<terms>
    <item>
        <title>Use aria2c</title>
        <p>Parabolic will use aria2c instead of yt-dlp's native downloader.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Predefinito: Disattivato</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Numero Massimo di Connessioni Per Server</title>
        <p>This option only applies when using aria2c is enabled. This option is the same as the <code>-x</code> flag passed to aria2c.</p>
        <p>Il numero massimo di connessioni per server utilizzabile. Deve essere un valore intero compreso tra 1 e 32.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Predefinito: 16</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Dimensione minima divisa</title>
        <p>This option only applies when using aria2c is enabled. This option is the same as the <code>-k</code> flag passed to aria2c.</p>
        <p>La taglia minima, in MiB, in cui dividere un file. Deve essere un valore intero compreso tra 1 e 1024.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Predefinito: 20</p>
        </note>
    </item>
</terms>
